::Firearm::

Firearm enters the bridge of the Cybertronian Fire (Necromancer presumably 
following him), going over to one of the scanners. He taps a few keys, 
bringing up Hell Drak's reading when the ship had scanned her during their 
arrival.

He presses another button, initiating a planetary scan for her.

"It'll pick her up in a little while, then we can run the rescue mission," he 
says, looking at the scanners.
